eter|year=1997|title=Introduction|url=|journal=Landmark Trust Newsletter \u2013 Autumn 1997|volume=|pages=|via=}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Appleton Water Tower]]\n|[[File:Appleton Water Tower - geograph.org.uk - 1022651.jpg|195x195px]]\n|[[Sandringham, Norfolk|Sandringham]]\n|Norfolk\n|1976\n|1977\n|\n|-\n|Cavendish Hall\n|\n|[[Cavendish, Suffolk|Cavendish]]\n|Suffolk\n|2010\n|2010\n|\n|-\n|[[Freston Tower]]\n|[[File:Freston tower4.jpg|160x160px]]\n|Ipswich\n|Suffolk\n|2001\n|2005\n|\n|-\n|Houghton West Lodge\n|\n|[[Houghton, Norfolk|Houghton]]\n|Norfolk\n|1990\n|1996\n|\n|-\n|Keeper's Cottage\n|\n|Shuttleworth\n|Bedfordshire\n|2004\n|2007\n|\n|-\n|Lynch Lodge\n|[[File:Lynch Lodge - geograph.org.uk - 265413.jpg|120x120px]]\n|Alwalton, near Peterborough\n|Cambridgeshire\n|1983\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Manor Farm, Diss|Manor Farm]]\n|[[File:ManorFarm.JPG|120x120px]]\n|[[Pulham Market]], near Diss\n|Norfolk\n|1979\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Martello tower|Martello Tower]]\n|[[File:Aldeburgh Martello Tower front.jpg|120x120px]]\n|[[Aldeburgh]]\n|Suffolk\n|1971\n|\n|\n|-\n|Methwold Old Vicarage\n|[[File:House opposite St George's Church, Methwold, Norfolk - geograph.org.uk - 312484.jpg|120x120px]]\n|[[Methwold]]\n|Norfolk\n|1998\n|2002\n|\n|-\n|New Inn\n|\n|[[Peasenhall]]\n|Suffolk\n|1971\n|\n|Three separate lets prior to refurbishment in 2013\n|-\n|Peake's House\n|\n|[[Colchester]]\n|Essex\n|1995\n|1995\n|\n|-\n|Purton Green\n|[[File:Purton Green Farm - geograph.org.uk - 916546.jpg|120x120px]]\n|Stansfield\n|Suffolk\n|1969\n|1971\n|\n|-\n|Queen Anne's Summerhouse\n|\n|Shuttleworth, Old Warden\n|Bedfordshire\n|2004\n|2009\n|\n|-\n|Stoker's Cottage\n|\n|[[Stretham Old Engine|Stretham]]\n|Cambridgeshire\n|2005\n|2007\n|\n|-\n|Warden Abbey\n|[[File:Warden Abbey (428017).jpg|120x120px]]\n|Old Warden\n|Bedfordshire\n|1974\n|1976\n|Remodelled 2017\n|-\n|The Warren House\n|\n|[[Kimbolton, Cambridgeshire|Kimbolton]]\n|Cambridgeshire\n|2004\n|2012\n|\n|}\n\n====North of England====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"