-\n| align=\"left\" |Peters Tower\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:Lympstone clock tower - geograph.org.uk - 1208469.jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Lympstone]]\n| align=\"left\" |Devon\n| align=\"center\" |1979\n| align=\"center\" |\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |Pond Cottage\n| align=\"left\" |\n| align=\"left\" |Endsleigh, near [[Tavistock, Devon|Tavistock]]\n| align=\"left\" |Devon\n| align=\"center\" |1983\n| align=\"center\" |1984\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |The Priest's House\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:The Priest House, Holcombe Rogus (geograph 2508361).jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Holcombe Rogus]]\n| align=\"left\" |Devon\n| align=\"center\" |1984\n| align=\"center\" |\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Robin Hood's Hut]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:Robin Hood's Hut above Halswell House - geograph.org.uk - 577854.jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Halswell House|Halswell]], [[Goathurst]]\n| align=\"left\" |Somerset\n| align=\"center\" |2000\n| align=\"center\" |2004\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |Sanders\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:Sanders, Lettaford - geograph.org.uk - 134003.jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |Lettaford, [[North Bovey]]\n| align=\"left\" |Devon\n| align=\"center\" |1976\n| align=\"center\" |1978\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Shute Gatehouse]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:Shute Gatehouse - geograph.org.uk - 864320.jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |Near [[Axminster]]\n| align=\"left\" |Devon\n| align=\"center\" |1978\n| align=\"center\" |\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Silverton Park|Silverton Park Stables]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:StableBlock_SilvertonPark_Devon.JPG|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Silverton, Devon|Silverton]]\n| align=\"left\" |Devon\n| align=\"center\" |1987\n| align=\"center\" |2008\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Stogursey Castle]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:Stogursey Castle - geograph.org.uk - 215767.jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Stogursey]], [[Bridgwater]]\n| align=\"left\" |Somerset\n| align=\"center\" |1982\n| align=\"center\" |1983\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Swiss Cottage, Devon|Swiss Cottage]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:Swiss Cottage Endsleigh. - geograph.org.uk - 468001.jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |Endsleigh, near [[Tavistock, Devon|Tavistock]]\n| align=\"left\" |Devon\n| align=\"center\" |1977\n| align=\"center\" |\n| align=\"left\" |<small>Designed by [[Jeffrey Wyatville]]</small>\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |The Wardrobe\n| align=\"left\" |\n| align=\"left\" |[[Salisbury]]\n| align=\"left\" |Wiltshire\n| align=\"center\" |1979\n| align=\"center\" |\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Whiteford Temple]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:Whiteford Temple.jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Callington, Cornwall|Callington]]\n| align=\"left\" |Cornwall\n| align=\"center\" |1984\n| align=\"center\" |\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n|Winsford Cottage Hospital\n|\n|Halwill Junction\n|Devon\n|\n|2019\n|Grade II* former Cottage Hospital designed by [[Charles Voysey (architect)|CFA Voysey]] in 1900, also on the Buildings at Risk register.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.halwill.org.uk/index.aspx?articleid=7418|title=CFA Voysey's Winsford Cottage Hospital|last=|first=|date=|website=Halwill.org.uk|accessdate=29 March 2017}}</ref>  After being declared surplus to needs by the NHS in 1999, the hospital was acquired by the Winsford Trust who gained some support for renovation from English Heritage and the [[Pilgrim Trust]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.winsfordtrust.com/winsford-cottage-hospital|title=About \u2013 The Winsford Trust|last=|first=|date=|website=winsfordtrust.com|accessdate=29 March 2017}}</ref>  Proposals for joint community use and a Landmark Trust holiday let were presented to the local community in November 2016.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/events/1840767046153232/|title=The Future of Winsford Hospital; Event \u2013 9 November 2016|last=|first=|date=|website=Facebook \u2013 The Winsford Trust, Halwill Junction|accessdate=29 March 2017}}</ref> On 8 June 2017 an appeal was launched to save the hospital by raising \u00a3355,000 within twelve months, adding to an initial \u00a396,000 grant from the [[Heritage Lottery Fund]] and money raised through other groups and supporters.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.landmarktrust.org.uk/Properties-list/winsford-cottage-hospital/Appeal/|title=Winsford Cottage Hospital|website=www.landmarktrust.org.uk|accessdate=5 August 2017}}</ref>  By April 2018, the appeal was within sight of its target, needing a final \u00a340,000 to unlock a total Heritage Lottery Fund grant of \u00a3486,000.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.landmarktrust.org.uk/Properties-list/winsford-cottage-hospital/Appeal/|title=Winsford Cottage Hospital|website=www.landmarktrust.org.uk|accessdate=24 May 2018}}</ref>  The Trust announced on 19 July 2018 the full required sum of \u00a31.5m had been raised, with restoration work scheduled to start during the summer.\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |Wolveton Gatehouse\n| align=\"left\" |\n| align=\"left\" |Near [[Dorchester, Dorset|Dorchester]]\n| align=\"left\" |Dorset\n| align=\"center\" |\n| align=\"center\" |\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Woodsford|Woodsford Castle]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:Woodsford Castle - geograph.org.uk - 1288442.jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |Near [[Dorchester, Dorset|Dorchester]]\n| align=\"left\" |Dorset\n| align=\"center\" |1977\n| align=\"center\" |1992\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Woodspring Priory]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:WoodspringPrioryFront081006.jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |Near [[Weston-super-Mare]]\n| align=\"left\" |Somerset\n| align=\"center\" |1969\n| align=\"center\" |1992\n| align=\"left\" |Priory Church, Infirmary and Farmhouse acquired from National Trust, 1969.  Restoration completed in phases:<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Crook|first=C D|year=1991|title=The Repair and Restoration of Woodspring Priory|url=|journal=Landmark Trust 