e_House_south_side.JPG|120px]]\n|align=left|[[Aston Munslow]]\n|align=left|Shropshire\n|align=center|1990\n|align=center|1991\n|align=left|\n|-\n|}\n\n====Southwest====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto;\"\n|+\n|-\n!|Name\n!class=\"unsortable\"|Image\n!|Town\n!|County\n!|Acquired\n!|Opened for lets\n!class=\"unsortable\"|Notes\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |Anderton House\n| align=\"left\" |\n| align=\"left\" |[[Goodleigh]]\n| align=\"left\" |Devon\n| align=\"center\" |2000\n| align=\"center\" |2003\n| align=\"left\" |Architect: Peter Adlington, 1969\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |Arra Venton\n| align=\"left\" |\n| align=\"left\" |[[Porthmeor|Lower Porthmeor]]\n| align=\"left\" |Cornwall\n| align=\"center\" |\n| align=\"center\" |1991<ref>{{Cite journal|last=|first=|year=1992|title=Arra Venton|url=|journal=Landmark Trust Newsletter \u2013 Spring 1992|volume=|pages=|via=}}</ref>\n| align=\"left\" |First listed as opening in 1989<ref name=\":0\" />\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Beckford's Tower]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:Beckford's_Tower_-_geograph.org.uk_-_746959.jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Bath, Somerset|Bath]]\n| align=\"left\" |Somerset\n| align=\"center\" |2000\n| align=\"center\" |2000\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Belmont, Lyme Regis|Belmont]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:Belmont_House.JPG|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Lyme Regis]]\n| align=\"left\" |Dorset\n| align=\"center\" |2006\n| align=\"center\" |2015\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Bridge Cottage, Peppercombe|Bridge Cottage]]\n| align=\"left\" |\n| align=\"left\" |[[Peppercombe]]\n| align=\"left\" |Devon\n| align=\"center\" |1988\n| align=\"center\" |\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[The Captain's House, Cornwall|The Captain's House]]\n| align=\"left\" |\n| align=\"left\" |[[Porthmeor|Lower Porthmeor]]\n| align=\"left\" |Cornwall\n| align=\"center\" |1995\n| align=\"center\" |1995\n| align=\"left\" |Previously leased to [[National Trust for Places of Histori