\n| align=\"center\" |1968\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Crownhill Fort]]\n| align=\"left\" |\n| align=\"left\" |[[Plymouth]]\n| align=\"left\" |Devon\n| align=\"center\" |1987\n| align=\"center\" |1995\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |Danescombe Mine\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:Cothele Consols Engine House - geograph.org.uk - 926058.jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Calstock]]\n| align=\"left\" |Cornwall\n| align=\"center\" |1972\n| align=\"center\" |1973\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n|Dunshay Manor\n|\n|Worth Matravers\n|Dorset\n|2006\n|2019\n|Bequeathed to the Trust in 2006 by [[Mary Spencer Watson]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/news/2006/mar/18/guardianobituaries.artsobituaries|title=Obituary: Mary Spencer Watson|last=Morley|first=Brian|date=18 March 2006|website=the Guardian|accessdate=24 May 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2008/jul/14/law.theatre|title=Actor loses court battle over \u00a32.3m estate of mother's lesbian lover|last=Lewis|first=Paul|date=14 July 2008|website=the Guardian|accessdate=24 May 2018}}</ref>  Initially part of the Trust's Legacy Estate, proposed for a 20-year lease from 2013, much repair work was undertaken in the subsequent four years.  In Spring 2018 the Trust announced further renovation would take place during the Summer to enable the Manor to be available for lets from 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.landmarktrust.org.uk/news-and-events/latest-news/dunshay-manor-update/?spMailingID=34407287&spUserID=MTE4NDEyOTg5NzAzS0&spJobID=1282655427&spReportId=MTI4MjY1NTQyNwS2|title=Dunshay Manor Update {{!}} The Landmark Trust|website=www.landmarktrust.org.uk|accessdate=24 May 2018}}</ref>  Bookings for the manor from May 2019 onwards were opened on 9 March 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/LandmarkTrust/status/1103958597363486720|title=Bookings for our latest property Dunshay Manor go live tomorrow at 9am, for Friends of Landmark. Find out how to become a Friend here: http://ow.ly/cr8L50mMxbB\u00a0pic.twitter.com/HJo3oVguyE|last=Trust|first=The Landmark|date=2019-03-08|website=@LandmarkTrust|language=en|access-date=2019-03-19}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Egyptian House, Penzance|The Egyptian House]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:Egyptian_house,_Chapel_Street,_Penzance,_close_up.jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Penzance]]\n| align=\"left\" |Cornwall\n| align=\"center\" |1968\n| align=\"center\" |1971\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |Elton House\n| align=\"left\" |\n| align=\"left\" |[[Bath, Somerset|Bath]]\n| align=\"left\" |Somerset\n| align=\"center\" |1982\n| align=\"center\" |1996\n| align=\"left\" |Bequeathed by Philippa Savery, 1982<ref>{{Cite journal|last=|first=|year=1996|title=A Gift to Landmark|url=|journal=Landmark Trust Newsletter \u2013 Spring 1996|volume=|pages=|via=}}</ref>\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |The Farmhouse\n| align=\"left\" |\n| align=\"left\" |[[Porthmeor|Lower Porthmeor]]\n| align=\"left\" |Cornwall\n| align=\"center\" |\n| align=\"center\" |\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |Frenchman's Creek\n| align=\"left\" |\n| align=\"left\" |[[Helford]]\n| align=\"left\" |Cornwall\n| align=\"center\" |1987\n| align=\"center\" |1990\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Gurney Manor]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:Gurney Manor.jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Cannington, Somerset|Cannington]]\n| align=\"left\" |Somerset\n| align=\"center\" |1984\n| align=\"center\" |1992\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Kingswear Castle]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:Kingswear_Castle_from_Dartmouth_Castle.jpg|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |Near [[Dartmouth, Devon|Dartmouth]]\n| align=\"left\" |Devon\n| align=\"center\" |1987\n| align=\"center\" |1990\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |The Library\n| align=\"left\" |[[File:PalladianLibraryStevenstoneDevon.JPG|120px]]\n| align=\"left\" |[[Stevenstone]]\n| align=\"left\" |Devon\n| align=\"center\" |1978\n| align=\"center\" |\n| align=\"left\" |\n|-